# SkillSetGo POS — Finalized Implementation Plan (V1)

An offline-first POS & restaurant management system built with Vite+React PWA, PouchDB↔CouchDB sync, CouchDB→PostgreSQL event projection, Capacitor Android wrapper, and proprietary hardware integrations (Virtual Soundbox via TTS & Bluetooth Thermal Printing).

---

## Locked-In V1 Scope Summary

| Decision | Resolution |
|----------|------------|
| **Frontend** | Vite + React SPA (not Next.js) |
| **Cloud DB** | CouchDB (sync) + PostgreSQL (analytics/reporting/webhook state) |
| **Soundbox offline behavior** | Auto-fire on sync if party already Seated |
| **Multi-outlet** | `outlet_id` partitioning from Day 1 |
| **Digital Menu** | Full customer PWA: Browse → Cart → Pay via Razorpay |
| **GST** | Full CGST+SGST+IGST line-item breakdown; e-invoicing deferred to V2 |
| **Aggregators (Swiggy/Zomato)** | Deferred to V2 |
| **KDS** | Deferred to V1.5; V1 uses printed KOTs only |
| **Auth** | Cloud login (Email/OTP) for managers + locally cached PINs for staff |
| **Inventory** | SKU-level stock counts only; recipe auto-deduction deferred to V2 |
| **Soundbox audio** | Native Android TTS engine (multi-dialect dynamic strings) |

