## WS4: Backend Webhooks & State Machine

### 4.1 Conditional Soundbox — State Machine

```
CONDITION A: party.payment_received === true    (Razorpay webhook)
CONDITION B: party.status === "seated"          (Staff on POS device)
GUARD:       party.soundbox_triggered === false  (Prevent double-fire)
```

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> QUEUED: Customer joins queue<br/>+ optionally orders on digital menu

    QUEUED --> QUEUED_PAID: Razorpay webhook<br/>payment.captured
    QUEUED --> SEATED_UNPAID: Staff marks Seated

    QUEUED_PAID --> TRIGGER_ZONE: Staff marks Seated
    SEATED_UNPAID --> TRIGGER_ZONE: Razorpay webhook<br/>payment.captured

    state TRIGGER_ZONE {
        [*] --> Evaluate
        Evaluate --> FireEvents: A AND B AND NOT triggered
        FireEvents --> MarkTriggered
        MarkTriggered --> [*]
    }

    TRIGGER_ZONE --> ACTIVE: Soundbox + KOT fired

    ACTIVE --> BILLING: Staff opens bill
    BILLING --> CLOSED: Settlement complete

    note right of TRIGGER_ZONE
        Fires BOTH:
        1. WebSocket → TTS announcement
        2. WebSocket → KOT print
    end note
```

### 4.2 Offline Auto-Fire on Reconnect

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant CUST as Customer
    participant RZ as Razorpay
    participant BE as Backend
    participant COUCH as CouchDB
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant PDB as PouchDB (Offline!)
    participant POS as POS Staff

    CUST->>RZ: Pay via digital menu
    RZ->>BE: payment.captured webhook
    BE->>COUCH: party.payment_received = true
    BE->>PG: pg_party_state: payment_received = true
    Note over PDB: DEVICE IS OFFLINE

    POS->>PDB: Mark party "seated" (LOCAL only)
    Note over PDB: status=seated, payment_received=false<br/>(stale — hasn't synced yet)

    Note over PDB,COUCH: 📶 Network restored

    PDB->>COUCH: Push: status = "seated"
    COUCH->>PDB: Pull: payment_received = true

    Note over COUCH: Both conditions now present<br/>in merged document

    COUCH->>BE: _changes feed: party doc updated
    BE->>BE: checkAndTriggerSoundbox()
    BE->>POS: WebSocket: SOUNDBOX_TRIGGER
    BE->>POS: WebSocket: KOT_TRIGGER
    POS->>POS: 🔊 TTS: "Payment received..."
    POS->>POS: 🖨️ KOT prints

    Note over BE: Auto-fired on sync,<br/>no staff re-trigger needed
```

