## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

```bash
# Shared package — schema validation, GST calc, ULID
npm run test --workspace=packages/shared

# POS app — PouchDB hooks, conflict resolution, services
npm run test --workspace=apps/pos

# Backend — webhook handler, state machine, projector
npm run test --workspace=backend

# Integration — PouchDB ↔ CouchDB sync round-trip
npm run test:integration --workspace=apps/pos

# E2E — critical user flows (Playwright)
npm run test:e2e --workspace=apps/pos
```

### Manual Verification

| Test Case | Method |
|-----------|--------|
| Offline billing | Airplane mode → create order → bill → print → reconnect → verify sync to CouchDB + PG |
| Soundbox conditional trigger | Pay via digital menu → verify NO sound → mark Seated → verify TTS plays |
| Soundbox offline auto-fire | Pay online → go offline → mark Seated offline → reconnect → verify auto-fire |
| KOT printing | Connect BT printer → place order → verify KOT prints with correct layout |
| Conflict resolution | Two tablets add items to same order offline → reconnect → verify merge |
| GST breakdown | Create order with mixed tax items → verify CGST/SGST breakdown on bill |
| Digital menu flow | QR scan → browse → cart → Razorpay pay → verify party updated |
| PWA install | Chrome → Add to Home Screen → offline launch → verify app shell loads |
| TTS multi-language | Switch TTS to Hindi → trigger payment → verify Hindi announcement |
| Device registration | Fresh install → assign device code → verify unique bill numbering |
